stories.text:
Happy Telehealth Awareness Week!

I'm working on a next generation health tech product to help people have easier access to doctors, make an informed choice prior making an appointment with their doctor. Chronic conditions can be difficult to manage and patients need to discover alternative tactics and solutions changing their lifestyle.

I'm launching a product feature for people with chronic conditions to ask questions anonymously (if they wish) and request answers from doctors.

Please sign up if you'd like to participate in the private beta of the product! https://gdltpakxcad.typeform.com/to/ZfRm3K7P

For an infographic on problematic statistics in the state of healthcare today, please view here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rJ24mRncUbe9_iylZ3hHZ6640_VUghVt/view?usp=sharing

For an infographic on how the product feature works, please view here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MsfN1MZABYArKxPaVfZf2GdGMpALuiPT/view?usp=sharing

Any questions and concerns, please let me know!
